@yasserogier As per Neil there was a file but that was for him to see who was assigned to the upliftment agent company. He has provided the names that need to move to companies in the log. If you require more than just names, please let me know what fields you require. User fields are different to company fields.

He advises that he did specify the report changes. They need to be broken up by company. Not sure how else to explain that.
